g.text: Smoothed line is from a generalized additive model, and is used to adjust incidence numbers before analysis to
estimate effective reproduction number. The lowest rate is 0.07%, and a positivity rate of 1.5% would result
in adjusted case numbers being 1.35 times their raw value.
Covid-19 test positivity in Victoria, Australia, 2020
Data gathered by The Guardian; analysis by http://freerangestats.info. Last updated 2020-08-02.
